{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-jsx","path":"/CRA로 Typescript 세팅하기/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Pang's Blog"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"5750f348-7689-5d45-8c43-6a5aa6406f59","excerpt":"CRA로 TypeScript와 React, CSS로 TailwindCSS를 세팅해보자. 1. Create React App(CRA)  2. TailwindCSS 설치하기 \nor\n 으로 패키지를 개발 종속성으로 추가한다. 3. TailwindCSS config 파일 초기화  4. TailwindCSS 적용 src/index.css 상단에 를 추가해준다.","html":"<p>CRA로 TypeScript와 React, CSS로 TailwindCSS를 세팅해보자.</p>\n<h2>1. Create React App(CRA)</h2>\n<blockquote>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">npx create-react-app 프로젝트명 --template typescript</code></p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2>2. TailwindCSS 설치하기</h2>\n<blockquote>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">yarn add -D tailwindcss postcss autoprefixer</code>\nor\n<code class=\"language-text\">npm i -D tailwindcss postcss autoprefixer</code></p>\n</blockquote>\n<ul>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">D 옵션</code>으로 패키지를 개발 종속성으로 추가한다.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>3. TailwindCSS config 파일 초기화</h2>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">yarn tailwind init -p</code></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>tailwind<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>config<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>js\n\nmodule<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>exports <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token literal-property property\">content</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n  \t<span class=\"token string\">\"./src/**/*.{js,jsx,ts,tsx}\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token comment\">// src 하위 파일 중 확장자가 .js,.jsx,.ts,.tsx인 파일을 대상으로 한다는 의미</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token literal-property property\">theme</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token literal-property property\">extend</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token literal-property property\">plugins</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<h2>4. TailwindCSS 적용</h2>\n<p>src/index.css 상단에</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token atrule\"><span class=\"token rule\">@tailwind</span> base<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token atrule\"><span class=\"token rule\">@tailwind</span> components<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token atrule\"><span class=\"token rule\">@tailwind</span> utilities<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></span></code></pre></div>\n<p>를 추가해준다.</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"TypeScript + TailwindCSS로 프로젝트 시작하기","date":"June 24, 2023","update":"June 24, 2023","tags":["ReactJS","TypeScript","CRA","TailwindCSS","Blog"],"series":"Project"},"fields":{"slug":"/CRA로 Typescript 세팅하기/","readingTime":{"minutes":0.74}}},"seriesList":{"edges":[{"node":{"id":"51ac987e-4d37-5389-9b14-8d38dd16b5e9","fields":{"slug":"/Typescript로 프로젝트 세팅하기/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"TypeScript로 프로젝트 세팅하기"}}},{"node":{"id":"5750f348-7689-5d45-8c43-6a5aa6406f59","fields":{"slug":"/CRA로 Typescript 세팅하기/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"TypeScript + TailwindCSS로 프로젝트 시작하기"}}},{"node":{"id":"6f1fdf6a-2274-5c5c-af76-5d322c7eb320","fields":{"slug":"/Typescript로 초기세팅하기/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"TypeScript로 진경옥몰 초기 세팅하기"}}},{"node":{"id":"6742a0c1-d3cc-54ec-8ee3-e3910a8531f3","fields":{"slug":"/PortOne사용하기/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Typescript & React PortOne으로 결제 테스트하기"}}},{"node":{"id":"970f8e13-d64c-5dd4-be56-f5904903fe1b","fields":{"slug":"/fullpage사용하기/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"fullpage.js 사용하기"}}}]},"previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/Typescript로 프로젝트 세팅하기/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"TypeScript로 프로젝트 세팅하기"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/Typescript로 초기세팅하기/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"TypeScript로 진경옥몰 초기 세팅하기"}}},"pageContext":{"id":"5750f348-7689-5d45-8c43-6a5aa6406f59","series":"Project","previousPostId":"51ac987e-4d37-5389-9b14-8d38dd16b5e9","nextPostId":"6f1fdf6a-2274-5c5c-af76-5d322c7eb320"}},"staticQueryHashes":[]}